{"tid":1373818,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[728上環見] 前綫手勢雛議","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T02:10:04.000Z","uid":81424,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cad3ed598f9ce979584dbcdd8bdbf0ba38f83319","tid":1373818,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:22:57.000Z","msg":"鑑於近排隻online game好多時前勢指令傳唔到去後方<br />\n所以有必要建立一套手勢去傳達前綫命令<br />\n所以小弟就拋磚引玉下<br />\n<br />\n1. 要求增緩<br />\n手勢：擧高雙手 手掌向前 隻手向前揮<br />\n口號：要增緩 要增緩<br />\n<br />\n2. 前進<br />\n手勢：一隻手放低 一隻手向前指<br />\n口號：前進 前進<br />\n<br />\n3. 死守<br />\n手勢：舉高雙手 大姆指向天指<br />\n口號：堅守 堅守<br />\n<br />\n4. 後退<br />\n手勢：一隻手放低 一隻手向後指<br />\n口號：退而不撤 退而不撤<br />\n<br />\n5. 撤退 (翻屋企)<br />\n手勢：兩隻手向後<br />\n口號：翻屋企 翻屋企<br />\n<br />\n(潰散就自己執生 後排記得要組防綫 同埋由其他大街小巷包抄敵人)<br />\n2 4 5 請同時配以實際行動 (e.g. 向後走 向前走)<br />\n<br />\n如果有其他建議歡迎提出<br />\n但「翻屋企」一定要由前綫講起<br />\n亂講死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfdc8fbd820b2795098d161bf5ba5f8a6d0d0f72","tid":1373818,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061dbdd44ead1f3154640d4513df8362d7b9f591","tid":1373818,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946c0c2e60c63d0f2a1b9684d87c18e3cb4f2e85","tid":1373818,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f761573b5e64495491f88f5f6ba966cbb36e73c","tid":1373818,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:25:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"138ded357d51b5095e282c1ea1beb43bdfe35027","tid":1373818,"uid":279266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:25:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"p